(this would mitigate suddenly finding something that teases you enough to dive into new production techniques and throwing the content delivery schedule out the window, in part due to feeling like the current 1 week schedule production techniques are 'getting old' and you wanna get out of the 'sucking loop')

i hope in no way does this come across as demanding because the 1 week schedule sounds remarkably brutal. i suppose the brutality could stem from the seemingly possible nature of it before every start. thinking just how possible some things can be can (on occasion) really be crippling huh
